SIMPLE: reexport
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Reexport
<hw>Re`ex*port"</hw> <pr>(-p?rt")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To export
again, as what has been imported.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reexport</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Reexport
<hw>Re*ex"port</hw> <pr>(r?*?ks"p?rt)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any
commodity reexported; -- chiefly in the plural.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Reexportation</ent>⟦br⟧
